Exercice:
Create a function that returns the total number of parameters passed in.
numberArgs("a", "b") ➞ 2
numberArgs(10, 20, 30, 40, 50,70) ➞ 6

function numberArgs (){        
  return arguments.length;
}
console.log(numberArgs(7, 7, "aazk""));
